title: [Ramshackle Hut, Interior]
description: Wide beams of light stream down through gaping holes in the wooden walls, illuminating a large chamber nearly covered with a thick layer of dust, dead leaves and other debris.  A stout birch pole rises up from the floor to the ceiling in the center of the room and from hooks along its sides dangle a half dozen cord leashes.  An animal musk hangs heavy in the still air, and numerous paw prints crisscross the dusty floor.

Wide beams of moonlight stream down through gaping holes in the wooden walls, dimly illuminating a large chamber nearly covered with a thick layer of dust, dead leaves and other debris.  A stout birch pole rises up from the floor to the ceiling in the center of the room and from hooks along its sides dangle a half dozen cord leashes.  An animal musk hangs heavy in the still air, and numerous paw prints crisscross the dusty floor.
